[10.103926, "o", "\r\nQ: heavy metals in food how big is the risk    [backend=bm25, vault=sample_vault]\r\n"]
[10.104292, "o", "\r\n[1] RFK - heavy metals in food  ›  RFK Jr. — \"heavy metals in our food\"   (score 6.649)\r\n    file: sample_vault/RFK - heavy metals in food.md\r\n"]
[10.104342, "o", "    Illustrative debate-prep note. The point of this note is the **magnitude** move: a claim can be *technically true* (trace heavy metals are detectable in some foods) while the implied magnitude (\"our food is poisoning kids\") is unsupported. Keep the actual numbers and the regulato…\r\n    citations (from this note):\r\n      • https://www.fda.gov/food/environmental-contaminants-food/closer-zero-reducing-childhood-exposure-contaminants-foods\r\n      • https://www.fda.gov/food/science-research-food/total-diet-study\r\n"]
[10.108703, "o", "\r\n"]
[12.309865, "o", "\u001b[2m# Different topic. Every answer comes back with its receipts attached.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
